page.title: 20Christian Names - W.Lough.
page.content: A survey was carried out at{Booth Wood Primary School to find the most popular names chosen by parents for their children.The age range of the children was 5-11 years.The class {registers}(nine in all) were checked by the children in the school and the following results obtained: {Lee}was the most popular{boys}name with{Mark}a close second.{Emma}was the most popular{girls}name, with{Emmily} and{Emilley}being two variations.The name{Michelle}was a close second, with {Michele}a single variation. { { { {TEXT compiled by:} St.Botolph's Primary School_ Shepshed. Booth Wood Primary School_ W.Lough. Garendon High School_ W.Lough.
